Yunnan: Coordinating the management of rural public welfare positions-Xinhua News Agency, Xinhua News Agency, Kunming, December 12 (Reporter Lin Bifeng) In order to continue to help the employment of poverty alleviation and consolidate the results of poverty alleviation, Yunnan Province recently introduced the public welfare nature of rural rejuvenation and rural areas.	 Job management related policies will help comprehensively promote rural revitalization.	 According to the relevant person in charge of the Yunnan Provincial Department of Human Resources and Social Security, at present, Yunnan has developed a total of 448,300 rural public welfare positions for employment in rural difficult groups such as poverty alleviation labor.	 Various public service capabilities play an important role.	 The new regulations were jointly issued by seven departments such as Yunnan people, rural revitalization, and finance, which mainly carried out uniform regulations on the scope, capital management, job development, and post management of the staff of rural public welfare positions at the grassroots level.	 In terms of post development and settings, the new rules are clear.	 "The principle is set. The recruitment procedures must be carried out in the steps such as announcement, declaration, review, publicity, employment, pre -job training and arrangement.	 In addition, the new regulations also clarify the specific responsibilities of the main development departments of rural public welfare positions, subsidy standards and subsidy methods for rural public welfare positions, and stipulate that the development department of rural public welfare positions should purchase accidental injury commercial insurance for rural public welfare positions.	 ; Requirements are required to supervise the issuance of subsidies for rural public welfare positions on a regular basis.
